Name: Yoshino
Phrase: This passage is smaller than originally thought. Butt and tail are doubly stuck inside.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: You should feel sorry for me instead, because every time you get stuck, I have to push you out with my face. I'm currently the only woman who has pressed her face into Yoshino's buttocks more than any other person in the world. So far.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Also, your tail! Do something about your wiggling tail! You've been tickling my nose for a while now and... ACHOO! I can't stop sneezing!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ah!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Hey! Don't stop suddenly!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: It's the exit, Yakutsk, Yoshino and friends have finally reached the finish line.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: For real!?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: But butt got caught again at the end. Squuuuish as much as you can, squish with your face, Yakutsk.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Bozhe, I can't help it then. Here I go, heave HO...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oooooh~!?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Phew, finally got out. That was a dai-dasshu.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Did we get out safely...?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...Does it look like it? It's darker than expected.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: This is a tochka after all. The structure is a bit different from the first one we found though...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: You can look out through this gap, right? Maybe it's to view towards the forest?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: You can also attack with weapons from here. There are traps and Phantom Mist, and while I admit that this is one of those ancient ruins, this place was definitely built as a military fortification.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I shudder to think of the enemy catching up with us in such a cramped underground fortress. It's just like the Loren Citadel's southern wall defence line...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yakutsk, Yoshino, if you made it to safety, please open the door.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Yes, yes, you can chat only after you've open these bars.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: H-Huh? It's closer than I thought.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Of course it is. I can see it from here.

Name: Putra
Phrase: By the way, we can hear your entire conversation coming out from the drain. 'The only woman who has pressed her face into Yoshino's buttocks more than any other person in the world', Yakutsk♪

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Yoshino! O-o-o-open the bars! You can open those bars in a flash, can't you?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Mhm. Can open it with a pop.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...Like this, open it with a pop.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: That's great, Yoshino. As a reward, I'm going to stroke your tail again.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: If possible, please wash it gently with warm water.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Oui, I'll wash you when I get some warm water.

Name: Amiens
Phrase: This place is also a stone fort then. Tochka? I think that's what they called it...

Name: Rouen
Phrase: It's bigger than the first one we found. It only has a small window, so it's dimly lit, but it's perfect to see what's going on outside.

Name: Rouen
Phrase: There's also a trench extending into the forest.

Name: Rouen
Phrase: We went through this area when we joined up from the gendarmerie station, didn't we? I don't remember there were any trenches.

Name: Amiens
Phrase: But we did go through here, this is where you, Rouen found that tall tree and said to jump from there.

Name: Amiens
Phrase: I'm sure neither the trench nor tochka... is here.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Ya two joined up just a few minutes ago, right? And in the meantime this tochka and trench appeared?

Name: Amiens
Phrase: I can only assume so. Neither Rouen nor I would ever get lost in these woods.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Does that mean that they have multiplied alongside the Phantom Mist...?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: If so, we need to remove the source of the Phantom Mist or it will get more and more out of control. It's very likely that this site itself is the source.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Queensway, what's wrong?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Um, I think I may have mistaken, but...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I see two boys in the woods.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: What the!? What are the Gendarmerie actually doing!?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Didn't they secure the whole area here before the investigation mission? Or are you saying that those two little guys got past the gendarmerie and approached these ruins?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I knew I wasn't mistaken. It's two boys. One big boy and one little boy... they are probably siblings.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: They could be attacked by the Mist Monster at any moment. We have to warn them of the danger and rescue them quickly!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: We can get in and out of the trench there. Let's temporarily suspend the investigation of the ruins and give priority to the protection of those children.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Stop, stop. Everyone, calm down.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...is what Shashou is trying to say.
I was just about to say that, but Yoshino beat me to it.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ufufu, it's not much~

Nobody knows for sure what will happen inside the Mist. If you charge in without thinking, you will put your life in danger. I'm sure you've all learnt about that in school, and I'm sure you've learnt it on every mission you've ever been on.
Naturally, the safety of those two boys is our top priority. But I want you to think about this situation once more.

Mysterious fortress ruins that appear with Phantom Mist and multiplied in a short time. Ever since the appearance of these ruins, we have been fighting Mist Monsters all the time. It is possible that while we are fighting, more Phantom Mist may also be forming in the forest, and the gendarmerie may be fighting them.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Could it be that the battles caused an breach in the surveillance network and that allowed those brothers to enter?

Do you think we would be observing such a calm scene from this tochka if the battle had occurred to the extent that the surveillance network breached? If there is a battle going on, and two boys made their way through the forest undetected... Don't you find all that strange?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: That's...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Everyone, remember what we experienced in Nishiki. Anything that appears in a place where there is Mist is suspicious.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yoshino...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yes, Yoshino is right. Conductor, let's send out scouts. We'll take a small group of people to those kids so that we can move quickly, and if everything is fine, we'll bring them to this tochka.
That would be good. It's better to minimise the risk.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Then, Yoshino will go sekkou. We'll susumu the zangou so so so sooo fast.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I'm worried about Yoshino alone, so I'll go too.
Yoshino and Yakutsk will be in charge of scouting then. If you see anything unusual, let us know immediately. All of us here will go to you.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Try not to get too far away from us. If a battle suddenly breaks out, stay within distance so that I can get to you immediately.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: In case of emergency, I will blow this whistle to let you know. Blowing once for 'Phantom Mist'. Twice for 'Requesting reinforcements'. If I blow only once, don't come. Because we will retreat immediately.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Understood. Take care of yourselves.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Now then, Yoshino, let's move. This time I'll take the lead.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ooooh-, are you tired of Yoshino's butt?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I won't let you off free if you get your ears or tail stuck again. Prioritize haste. I'm serious.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Okay. Let's show them how quick us two little girls are.
